Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.40,0:05:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.71,0:05:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些是必要的支出
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.03,0:05:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照這樣進行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.36,0:05:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.69,0:05:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的抽水機噪音相當大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.15,0:05:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼去咨詢製造商…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.44,0:05:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有預算  停用一台
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.78,0:05:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後把零件挪用到其他兩台上去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.54,0:05:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.81,0:05:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  要是有個萬一…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那時候再說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.88,0:05:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解了  老大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.54,0:05:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.86,0:05:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,商品的存放位置不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.47,0:05:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡空著呢  全部搬過去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.23,0:05:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警備用的器材損壞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  修好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.29,0:05:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食堂的韭菜炒肝不好吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.54,0:05:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.40,0:05:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超人氣偶像被發現在外過夜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.14,0:05:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種雜誌趕緊扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.05,0:06:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來還有什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.21,0:06:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些文件的處理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.89,0:06:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及協商對娛樂設施的翻新
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,協商?跟誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.04,0:06:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫夫路  馬卡龍  堤拉米三人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.26,0:06:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.42,0:06:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.40,0:06:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天已經累了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.14,0:06:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有力氣去跟那三個笨蛋攪合了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.41,0:06:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,處理文件更省力一些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.26,0:06:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.84,0:06:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  千斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.25,0:06:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,處理的盡量圓滑一些  圓滑一些哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.18,0:06:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你多說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.77,0:06:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  千斗你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.60,0:06:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是奇怪的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.85,0:06:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.93,0:06:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門開著呢  進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.91,0:06:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.29,0:06:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.78,0:06:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有點麻煩的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.00,0:07:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想讓可兒江先生您聽一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在正忙著處理文件呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.49,0:07:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能跟千斗說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.75,0:07:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊不聽所以才只能跟你說的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.61,0:07:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  沒有  不是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.73,0:07:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想直接跟可兒江先生您商量下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.00,0:07:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說到底什麼事兒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  趕緊說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.99,0:07:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼說明呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.30,0:07:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他直接看看比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.25,0:07:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這樣比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.83,0:07:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能稍微佔用點您的時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看這個  破破爛爛的了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.84,0:07:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能給點購置新器材的預算啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.25,0:07:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否決  你也知道現在資金不足吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.73,0:07:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  這樣的水槍會讓客人失望的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.83,0:07:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的任務就是解決這個事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.58,0:07:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請全力迎擊客人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎擊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:07:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種子彈倒是有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.39,0:08:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看這個  破破爛爛的了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.55,0:08:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買個新的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.26,0:08:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否決
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.28,0:08:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用別的器材來代替吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.15,0:08:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  這樣下去客人們都會逃走的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人要是逃了  就全力追擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.07,0:08:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追擊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.22,0:08:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請拿出全力認真處理  知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.97,0:08:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.45,0:08:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事就說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.01,0:08:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.55,0:08:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.73,0:08:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會說話的花  破破爛爛的了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.64,0:08:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.31,0:08:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否決
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.35,0:08:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自行處理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.83,0:08:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自行處理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.14,0:08:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多事都不好拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們商量什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.15,0:08:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰巧遇到而已  碰巧啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.25,0:08:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是偶然碰到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:09:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼不滿可以跟我說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.35,0:09:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過請不要去煩他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.76,0:09:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  不是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.79,0:09:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千斗  過來下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.76,0:09:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你說過要處理的圓滑一些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.77,0:09:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應你的要求  我圓滑的處理了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡圓滑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.35,0:09:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用槍威脅  讓對方服從
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.48,0:09:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣不是跟請我過來的時候一樣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.27,0:09:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要去威脅他們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.78,0:09:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡量找到兩全的辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.27,0:09:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用高壓讓他們服從絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也是採用高壓政策嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.43,0:09:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.44,0:09:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我讓他們認同了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.04,0:09:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會就這樣做了一年的代理經理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.08,0:09:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.68,0:09:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.11,0:09:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你現在是我的秘書
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.04,0:09:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣扯我的後腿  我可受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.66,0:09:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說我扯你後腿?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:09:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是照那樣下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.14,0:10:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你說  我還能怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.31,0:10:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千斗…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.49,0:10:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  千斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.56,0:10:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.64,0:10:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.38,0:10:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉媞琺  身體怎麼樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.35,0:10:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是可兒江大人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.59,0:11:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我還以為是五十鈴小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.91,0:11:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好些了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.47,0:11:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.38,0:11:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有點無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.24,0:11:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以剛想去外面吹吹風呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.82,0:11:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  這樣說不定也挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.84,0:11:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可兒江大人  能陪我一會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.39,0:11:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很舊  但是這個摩天輪很棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.12,0:11:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.08,0:11:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前就想請你來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.51,0:11:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺像是約會一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.78,0:11:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.38,0:11:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  能看見正門了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.76,0:11:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊是世外桃源呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.77,0:11:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那前面是野性之谷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.32,0:11:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.25,0:11:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.81,0:11:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  風景絕佳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.06,0:11:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成你懼高…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.86,0:11:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.01,0:11:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得我這樣的人會懼高嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.23,0:12:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可兒江大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.01,0:12:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.90,0:12:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.30,0:12:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懼高
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.14,0:12:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.80,0:12:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜下心來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.60,0:12:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道就不邀請您來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.34,0:12:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的虛榮和倔強造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.33,0:12:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.03,0:12:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.80,0:12:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  這件事請保密
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.59,0:12:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.98,0:12:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  還是告訴五十鈴小姐比較好…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.45,0:12:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對要保密
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.83,0:12:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.38,0:12:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  有點好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.96,0:13:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  拉媞琺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.28,0:13:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.25,0:13:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們曾經見過面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和可兒江大人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.81,0:13:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我記不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.70,0:13:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真和平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以防萬一要監視一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結界外是很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.43,0:13:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是在意她和可兒江二人獨處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.64,0:13:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的雨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.46,0:14:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼大的雨很少見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.55,0:14:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧這場雨  可以悠閒一陣了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得倒輕鬆  客人是零啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繆絲妹妹  你是水精靈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想辦法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.02,0:14:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦  水雜技我倒是很在行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.40,0:14:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次又怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.39,0:14:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.99,0:14:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.40,0:14:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生鏽了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.57,0:14:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排水設備…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.65,0:14:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場大雨讓這堆破爛罷工了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.51,0:14:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去地下設施會被水淹沒的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.80,0:14:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.08,0:14:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重大打擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.57,0:14:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會一個月不能營業的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.64,0:14:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會在這種時候故障
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.26,0:14:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大將  昨天跟你說過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.89,0:14:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說停掉一台
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.52,0:14:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  要是有個萬一…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.25,0:14:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此對剩下兩台增加了負擔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.71,0:14:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.86,0:14:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦  沒時間磨蹭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.75,0:15:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  對了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.08,0:15:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先轉移商品…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.70,0:15:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  比起這個職員的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  如果不在淹水之前阻止的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.36,0:15:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新營業之前一切就都完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.55,0:15:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,設立對策總部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.58,0:15:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.31,0:15:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來會議室
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.57,0:15:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.84,0:15:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將各處的消防抽水器配備到10個重要場所
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.78,0:15:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是音樂劇場班
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消防抽水器回收完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各排水班  在抽水器到達之前用水桶接力排水
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.44,0:15:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時用沙袋防止淹水擴大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.98,0:15:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是設備班
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.35,0:15:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第4通道的淹水已經阻止住了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.03,0:15:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續去第5通道的西邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.38,0:15:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.42,0:15:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抽水器配備完成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.98,0:15:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.50,0:15:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各班  開始排水
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.06,0:15:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.16,0:15:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請開始排水
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.55,0:15:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始排水
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.40,0:15:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始排水
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.71,0:15:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.67,0:16:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是元素之屋班
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.89,0:16:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一直在用水桶接力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.47,0:16:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請給這邊也送點抽水器來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.15,0:16:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抽水器全用在受災嚴重的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.37,0:16:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讓警備部過去支援
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.11,0:16:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大黑  你過去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.87,0:16:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.27,0:16:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再撐20分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.27,0:16:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法控制  我無法控制
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.78,0:16:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我死守
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.92,0:16:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs34}臨陣逃跑是要槍斃的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.60,0:16:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿修  換我來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.06,0:16:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去準備一下大家吃飯和休息的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.58,0:16:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總部  這裡是設備班
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.17,0:16:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排水設備修好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.14,0:16:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重複  排水設備修好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.93,0:17:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總部  明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.01,0:17:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.20,0:17:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  這是你的功勞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.52,0:17:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好  原經理代理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.32,0:17:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我回去工作了  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.23,0:17:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡似乎也沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.06,0:17:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.56,0:17:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是最後一處嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.97,0:17:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.97,0:17:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可兒江君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.10,0:17:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.52,0:17:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是對你不滿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.38,0:17:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.47,0:17:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.01,0:17:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你來這裡之前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.74,0:17:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這座遊樂園的代理經理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.07,0:17:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是一個只會用高壓態度命令職員的軍人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.60,0:17:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍人?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.25,0:17:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是近衛兵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.51,0:17:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家是武門世家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:17:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也毫無疑問地成為了軍人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.59,0:18:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這裡是因為上面命令我來重建遊樂園
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.61,0:18:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還真是輕率地命令啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.76,0:18:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實  我也知道這個任務不適合我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.91,0:18:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能辜負期待
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.23,0:18:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能竭盡全力不辱家名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.96,0:18:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果沒能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.51,0:18:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精英的第一次挫折嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.02,0:18:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挫折?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.51,0:18:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.63,0:18:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去在意家庭問題  逃走不就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千斗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.10,0:18:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  我從沒往這方面想過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.33,0:18:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.49,0:18:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  我失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.95,0:18:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道該如何面對這個事實
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.31,0:18:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,職員們也都討厭我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.04,0:19:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挫折的話  我也不輸給你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.11,0:19:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有懼高症
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.66,0:19:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我還是童星的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.80,0:19:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該…怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.80,0:19:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然害怕起高處了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.48,0:19:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.83,0:19:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是害怕讓父母失望  害怕失去人氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.79,0:19:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到現在還不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.33,0:19:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然那不是直接原因
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.29,0:19:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候我辭掉了藝人的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.64,0:19:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人斥責  令人失望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.76,0:19:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給各處都添了麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.46,0:19:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.84,0:19:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.02,0:19:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.87,0:19:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.10,0:20:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本大爺和你那小小的挫折
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.74,0:20:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是常有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.94,0:20:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然會為那種事情煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.09,0:20:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個人真無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.72,0:20:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.54,0:20:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太無聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.79,0:20:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  服了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.47,0:20:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.10,0:20:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定真是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.09,0:20:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.57,0:20:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.01,0:20:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你會對我說這些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.76,0:20:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.37,0:20:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.48,0:20:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.62,0:20:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.84,0:20:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  五十鈴小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.69,0:20:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害  五十鈴妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.08,0:20:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.00,0:20:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很累  總之謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.78,0:21:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才你說被他們討厭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.31,0:21:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在還這麼想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.95,0:21:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來
